<p class="link-more"><a href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/restaurant-ceo-priorities-evolving" class="more-link">Continue reading<span class="screen-reader-text"> "How Restaurant CEO Priorities are Evolving in 2020"</span></a></p>
<p>The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://aaronallen.com/blog/restaurant-ceo-priorities-evolving">How Restaurant CEO Priorities are Evolving in 2020</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://aaronallen.com">Aaron Allen &amp; Associates, Global Restaurant Consultants</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[		<div data-elementor-type="wp-post" data-elementor-id="15425" class="elementor elementor-15425">
						<div class="elementor-inner">
				<div class="elementor-section-wrap">
									<section class="elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-8ddc685 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default" data-id="8ddc685" data-element_type="section">
